00:04:43.120 --> 00:04:47.920
Kaashvi, aku muak berpura-pura.

00:04:49.400 --> 00:04:51.040
Mari kita akhiri sekarang.

00:04:54.280 --> 00:04:56.240
Saya telah menyimpan
surat cerai di sana.

00:04:59.080 --> 00:05:01.520
Tanda tangani mereka saat Anda menginginkannya.

00:05:02.880 --> 00:05:05.120
Beritahu dunia

00:05:05.720 --> 00:05:10.160
